   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Water for Learning in Kenyan &amp; Ugandan Schools</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will address the lack of clean water, hygiene and sanitation facilities in EPAfrica&apos;s partner schools in East Africa through investment in facilities to collect, store, clean and distribute water. Complementary hygiene and sanitation facilities such as handwashing stations and clothes washing stations may also be installed. This funding will enable us to improve the water situation in eight schools, directly impacting the health and education of at least 4,000 students.</narrative>
  </description>
